1
00:00:24,210 --> 00:00:24,980
[Minors]

2
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:26,790
[should watch with guardian consent]

3
00:00:28,290 --> 00:00:32,320
[The world is relative]

4
00:00:35,220 --> 00:00:37,300
[Adapted from a novel published on
Qidian Reading under China Literature]

5
00:00:37,320 --> 00:00:38,890
["Way of Choices" by Mao Ni]

6
00:00:40,250 --> 00:00:42,500
This is a story of a Little Taoist Monk
from the mountains

7
00:00:42,500 --> 00:00:45,850
who goes to Shendu to change his fate.

8
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:54,320
This is a story

9
00:00:54,350 --> 00:00:57,790
about the hope that we can all live
as we wish.

10
00:01:41,700 --> 00:01:43,000
[Shendu]

11
00:01:57,090 --> 00:01:58,870
[Guide to Shendu]

12
00:02:01,610 --> 00:02:05,020
[Shendu]

13
00:02:26,740 --> 00:02:31,260
[Way of Choices]

14
00:02:31,530 --> 00:02:34,390
[The Little Taoist Monk
has come down from the mountain]

15
00:02:32,110 --> 00:02:34,690
The Little Taoist Monk
has come down from the mountain.

16
00:02:34,420 --> 00:02:36,350
[The Young Director: Episode 1]

17
00:02:39,230 --> 00:02:41,390
[Shendu of the Great Zhou]

18
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,950
Goal number one:

19
00:02:42,970 --> 00:02:43,780
Tiandao Academy,

20
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:45,620
the finest academy in Shendu.

21
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:49,320
Those who can open the door
and enter the tower

22
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:51,250
will qualify for the written exam.

23
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,440
Look at that guy!

24
00:03:07,020 --> 00:03:09,200
You want to enter Tiandao Academy
without the Realm of Marrow Cleansing?

25
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:10,040
Idiot!

26
00:03:31,700 --> 00:03:32,470
Wait,

27
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:37,140
mot only has this one
not reached the Realm of Marrow Cleansing,

28
00:03:37,140 --> 00:03:39,940
he doesn't even have
basic Divine Consciousness!

29
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,440
I'm Chen Changsheng,

30
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:44,130
I have not yet begun my cultivation.

31
00:03:44,130 --> 00:03:45,680
That's why I wish to join the Academy.

32
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,560
Are you out of your mind?

33
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:50,060
[Zhongyu Tower]

34
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:50,220
This is the Tiandao Academy,
the number one!

35
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:52,640
You don't join to start cultivation,

36
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:54,079
only geniuses

37
00:03:54,079 --> 00:03:55,320
are allowed to join.

38
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,840
This idiot isn't listening?

39
00:04:00,670 --> 00:04:03,270
Let's bet how far he'll be blown away!

40
00:04:10,540 --> 00:04:11,700
Press it!

41
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:13,080
Are you scared?

42
00:04:12,420 --> 00:04:15,050
[Zhongyu Tower]

43
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:25,410
This formation disk is made of
Sensory Stone and Gale Array.

44
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:27,550
Sensory Stone absorbs True Essence,

45
00:04:27,550 --> 00:04:29,750
formation lines conduct True Essence,

46
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,720
and the core locks True Essence.

47
00:04:32,140 --> 00:04:34,420
If True Essence is not strong enough
to push the core open,

48
00:04:34,420 --> 00:04:36,150
it will trigger the Gale Array.

49
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:40,060
Only the North Wind Formation
from Liuzhou Qimen

50
00:04:40,060 --> 00:04:42,140
could have all these functions.

51
00:04:45,860 --> 00:04:47,520
I remember the solution is...

52
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:00,210
Jiao 3.

53
00:05:00,450 --> 00:05:01,130
Kang 7.

54
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:04,360
Di 6.

55
00:05:04,640 --> 00:05:05,470
Fang 4.

56
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:06,960
Xin 5.

57
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,400
Told you he's an idiot!

58
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:12,440
Pressing it like that
without even Divine Consciousness,

59
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:14,720
if it opens,
you can kick my head like a football!

60
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:15,480
Wei 1.

61
00:05:16,260 --> 00:05:16,990
Ji 9!

62
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,000
[Zhongyu Tower]

63
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:30,760
Senior,

64
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:31,560
it's a deal.

65
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,650
We'll count on your head
for tomorrow's game!

66
00:05:33,650 --> 00:05:34,860
That actually worked?

67
00:05:34,860 --> 00:05:36,990
He opened it without any cultivation!

68
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,760
What kind of sorcery is this?

69
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,120
Interesting.

70
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,840
You dare break the rules!

71
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:42,980
You want a beating?

72
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,640
Tang Thirty-Six, what are you doing?

73
00:05:48,630 --> 00:05:50,200
[Instructor Cao of Tiandao Academy]

74
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:50,900
Skipping class again?

75
00:05:52,180 --> 00:05:53,659
[Tang Thirty-Six,
Disciple of Tiandao Academy]

76
00:05:53,740 --> 00:05:54,480
Cao,

77
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,680
what are you doing?

78
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:57,360
Bullying someone with no cultivation...

79
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,040
Have you no shame?

80
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:58,400
You—

81
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,600
Cao,

82
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,680
don't be so hot-headed.

83
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:03,720
What's wrong?

84
00:06:03,150 --> 00:06:05,080
[Mao Qiuyu, Director of Tiandao Academy]

85
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:06,250
Director,

86
00:06:06,290 --> 00:06:09,770
this boy somehow found a way
to crack our mechanism.

87
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:11,600
He should be punished for cheating!

88
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,920
The notice says whoever opens the door
may enter the building,

89
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,640
it doesn't specify the method.

90
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:16,170
Exactly!

91
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:18,080
What notice?

92
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:19,410
That's just to fool the—

93
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,080
This formation disk was set

94
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:23,120
to filter out those in the Mortal Realm.

95
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,780
You haven't even reached
the Realm of Marrow Cleansing,

96
00:06:24,780 --> 00:06:26,650
you can't enter Tiandao Academy.

97
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,980
Filter out those in the Mortal Realm?

98
00:06:30,300 --> 00:06:31,280
If that's the case,

99
00:06:31,280 --> 00:06:32,610
why not state it openly?

100
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:34,460
A fake notice like this

101
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:36,260
only crushes people's hopes.

102
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:37,800
Besides,

103
00:06:40,390 --> 00:06:41,540
according to

104
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:44,290
Section 8, Article 4, Chapter 17
of the Academy Rules,

105
00:06:44,290 --> 00:06:46,570
the entrance exam is the only criteria,

106
00:06:44,610 --> 00:06:45,610
[Rules of Tiandao Academy]

107
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:48,280
not the Cleansing of Marrow.

108
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:51,770
There was a precedent set by the Bureau
eleven years ago.

109
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:52,800
Nonsense!

110
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:55,400
I've been teaching here for decades,

111
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:57,330
and I've never heard of such a rule!

112
00:06:57,880 --> 00:07:00,200
There is indeed such a rule.

113
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:03,320
You know quite a lot, little fellow.

114
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:04,760
Go on in.

115
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:07,980
Thank you, Senior.

116
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,450
And thank you

117
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,530
for just now.

118
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:12,200
No worries.

119
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:13,400
Go take your exam.

120
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:16,650
Then he can also take the written exam?

121
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:20,600
You—

122
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,400
Come along!

123
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:28,720
They actually let him in?

124
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,680
Right?

125
00:07:28,810 --> 00:07:31,340
[Zhongyu Tower]

126
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:31,280
That guy is quite something!

127
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:34,050
Has the bar for Tiandao Academy
been lowered?

128
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:37,600
It's the hardest exam in the Great Zhou.

129
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,280
Without Divine Consciousness,

130
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:41,210
how many books could you have read?

131
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:43,010
Goal number two:

132
00:07:43,010 --> 00:07:45,950
rank first
in Tiandao Academy's written exam.

133
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:52,600
There are 36 volumes for the Spring Exam
of Tiandao Academy.

134
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:55,280
The more volumes you complete,

135
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,560
the higher your score.

136
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:59,200
You have 15 minutes per volume.

137
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:00,480
Late submissions will be confiscated,

138
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,610
and you will be eliminated instantly.

139
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:03,920
Six hours later,

140
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:06,800
the top 30 will be admitted.

141
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,040
Weird.

142
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:11,120
Although
there are many kinds of questions,

143
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:14,120
they are all
in the Three Thousand Daoist Scriptures.

144
00:08:35,700 --> 00:08:38,530
Master never taught
Senior Yuren and me cultivation;

145
00:08:38,530 --> 00:08:40,460
he only had us study ancient texts.

146
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,640
Did he foresee this day?

147
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:56,600
It's 12:15 P.M.!

148
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:02,560
It's 12:30 P.M.!

149
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:08,840
It's 12:45 P.M.!

150
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:34,760
It's 2:30 P.M.!

151
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:48,400
Since the 36 Volumes were created,

152
00:09:48,420 --> 00:09:50,140
no one has ever finished them all.

153
00:09:50,140 --> 00:09:52,000
He finished in only three hours!

154
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,420
It seems Mr. Chen here

155
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:55,250
-will be the first of this year.
-The last person

156
00:09:55,250 --> 00:09:57,440
to enter the Academy as a mortal
was Wang Zhice, the legend.

157
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,970
Will he become a legend too?

158
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:02,650
Instructor Cao.

159
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:05,240
Isn't this Shuang'er
from the Divine General's Estate?

160
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:07,240
My Lady asked me to bring this to you.

161
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,560
Lady Xu?

162
00:10:13,340 --> 00:10:17,690
[The Spring Exam Results]

163
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:18,000
Thank you! I made the cut!

164
00:10:18,680 --> 00:10:19,720
Is your name...

165
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,880
Xiao Yichen?

166
00:10:21,610 --> 00:10:23,200
[The Spring Exam Results
Grade A Candidates]

167
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:23,440
My name is Chen Changsheng.

168
00:10:23,270 --> 00:10:25,280
[The Qualified List]

169
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:27,200
Chen Changsheng?

170
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:35,840
Sir,

171
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,840
I'd like to check my results.

172
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:39,000
Why?

173
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:40,800
My name is not on the list.

174
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:43,640
Who cares about your name?

175
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:46,120
And why should it be there?

176
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:49,140
Because he answered every question
correctly.

177
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:52,000
Don't meddle in this!

178
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:53,200
What a coincidence!

179
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:55,260
My hobby just happens to be meddling.

180
00:10:55,400 --> 00:10:56,730
Why isn't he on the list?

181
00:10:57,800 --> 00:10:58,760
It's none of your business!

182
00:10:58,760 --> 00:10:59,360
I—

183
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,320
I can't tell you.

184
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:01,840
Anyway,

185
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:03,440
you just can't join the Tiandao Academy!

186
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,240
What a hassle!

187
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:06,280
Running off because you know you're wrong?

188
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:07,160
I-I...

189
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:08,620
Take that, you old geezer!

190
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,000
Tang Thirty-Six,

191
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,920
how dare you disrespect your seniority!

192
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:13,240
You—

193
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:15,200
Thank you for your help.

194
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,720
If Tiandao Academy won't take me,

195
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:18,520
I'll just go to other academies.

196
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:20,320
You were rejected for no reason.

197
00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:21,560
Aren't you angry?

198
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,960
Anger is bad for the health.

199
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:23,960
It's not worth it.

200
00:11:25,760 --> 00:11:27,160
Besides, I have no desire

201
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:29,160
for a Tiandao Academy like this.

202
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:31,760
He really is an interesting guy.

203
00:11:34,220 --> 00:11:35,270
[A drink by the lotus pond
Would you fancy a cup?
Drunkenly, I mock the carp in the pond.]

204
00:11:35,290 --> 00:11:36,510
[Borrowing moonlight to buy wine;
stealing a lotus pod as a cup.]

205
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:41,480
I don't like Tiandao Academy either,

206
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:43,340
even though I'm a disciple there.

207
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:45,250
My name is Tang Thirty-Six.

208
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:46,400
C-H-E-N,

209
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:47,760
Chen Changsheng.

210
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:50,200
For a guy with such great learning,

211
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,800
your name is quite ordinary.

212
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,160
It has a good meaning.

213
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,200
As for your name...

214
00:11:56,560 --> 00:11:58,620
Are you the 36th child in your family?

215
00:11:59,910 --> 00:12:02,070
I'm ranked 36th on the Blue Cloud List.

216
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:03,620
I find it embarassing,

217
00:12:03,760 --> 00:12:05,690
so I changed my name to push myself.

218
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:06,960
The Blue Cloud List?

219
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:08,820
You don't know?

220
00:12:09,020 --> 00:12:17,760
[Blue Cloud List]

221
00:12:09,490 --> 00:12:10,420
[No. 5]

222
00:12:09,650 --> 00:12:12,170
It's the ranking list
for the young generation of the Great Zhou.

223
00:12:10,810 --> 00:12:12,230
[No. 4]

224
00:12:12,530 --> 00:12:13,960
[No. 3]

225
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:13,880
The higher you rank,

226
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:16,120
the better your chances to take
first place in the Imperial Court Exam.

227
00:12:14,280 --> 00:12:15,710
[No. 2]

228
00:12:16,210 --> 00:12:17,750
[No. 1]

229
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:23,770
The double-headed fish
is too cold in nature,

230
00:12:23,770 --> 00:12:25,700
the fish mint is bad for digestion,

231
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:27,440
the braised pork is too greasy.

232
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:29,770
And this sparrow and polygonatum soup...

233
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:31,720
It's nourishing in autumn and winter.

234
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:32,850
But it's spring now,

235
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:34,720
drinking it will cause internal heat.

236
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:35,280
Try it!

237
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:39,320
These are all signature dishes
I ordered from the nearby restaurants!

238
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,480
He is being so hospitable,

239
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,610
don't ruin the mood.

240
00:12:46,800 --> 00:12:49,120
It's tender but not greasy,
very delicious!

241
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:51,380
You don't look like someone from Shendu.

242
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:53,160
This is my first time here.

243
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:56,200
I studied medicine in Xining
with my Master.

244
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:57,840
Xining?

245
00:12:58,280 --> 00:12:59,920
The western edge of the Great Zhou.

246
00:12:59,920 --> 00:13:00,960
That's quite far.

247
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:04,050
Where are your parents?

248
00:13:05,520 --> 00:13:06,680
I have no parents.

249
00:13:08,880 --> 00:13:10,880
My Master and Senior raised me.

250
00:13:12,130 --> 00:13:13,160
Master said

251
00:13:13,180 --> 00:13:16,400
it was the coldest day in Yunmu Mountain.

252
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:39,000
The air was cold that day,

253
00:13:42,280 --> 00:13:43,680
and the water was, too.

254
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,480
But Senior Yuren's hands

255
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:52,700
were very warm.

256
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:14,860
Senior Yuren is the bravest person
in the world.

257
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:20,690
The Master who taught him

258
00:14:20,340 --> 00:14:22,360
[Taoist Monk Ji, Chen Changsheng's Master]

259
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:23,920
is naturally the most powerful.

260
00:14:35,340 --> 00:14:38,150
[The Old Temple of Xining]

261
00:14:49,680 --> 00:14:50,760
After saving me,

262
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:52,800
Master saw how sickly I was,

263
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:54,720
and named me Chen Changsheng

264
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:56,600
as a blessing for longevity.

265
00:14:58,020 --> 00:15:00,700
[Yuren, Chen Changsheng's Senior]

266
00:15:03,920 --> 00:15:05,980
Master never taught us cultivation,

267
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:12,580
only the Three Thousand Daoist Scriptures.

268
00:15:32,430 --> 00:15:33,190
So

269
00:15:33,590 --> 00:15:35,390
I read many, many books,

270
00:15:39,230 --> 00:15:41,030
all three thousand scriptures.

271
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:49,800
One day,

272
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:52,200
when the peach blossomed in Xining,

273
00:15:52,700 --> 00:15:54,720
a white crane
delivered a marriage contract.

274
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:56,160
Because my Master

275
00:15:56,520 --> 00:15:58,050
had saved her grandfather.

276
00:16:03,990 --> 00:16:07,070
[The Marriage Contract]

277
00:16:07,170 --> 00:16:08,760
[Yourong, Daughter of the Xu Family]

278
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:11,440
I am very curious

279
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:13,400
about what kind of person she is.

280
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:22,250
[Chen Changsheng]

281
00:16:22,650 --> 00:16:23,780
[Little Taoist Monk, if you ever come
to Shendu, you must come find me.]

282
00:16:23,800 --> 00:16:25,210
[There's so much delicious food here.
I'll take you for stewed beef bone.]

283
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:26,440
Little Taoist Monk,

284
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:28,400
when you grow up, come find me in Shendu.

285
00:16:28,400 --> 00:16:31,160
There are so many fun things
and delicious foods here.

286
00:16:31,160 --> 00:16:32,920
I'll take you to eat stewed beef bone,

287
00:16:32,920 --> 00:16:34,240
visit the Heavenly Book Mausoleum,

288
00:16:34,240 --> 00:16:36,240
and see the Bridge of Helplessness.

289
00:16:40,280 --> 00:16:43,410
That was the first time
I wanted to see the world outside.

290
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:45,320
But later...

291
00:17:03,850 --> 00:17:05,390
That was my first seizure.

292
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:07,160
Senior Yuren said

293
00:17:07,760 --> 00:17:10,420
the whole courtyard
was filled with fragrance.

294
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:17,960
Master,

295
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:20,400
my illness...

296
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:22,240
No doctor can cure it,

297
00:17:22,839 --> 00:17:24,170
no medicine can heal it.

298
00:17:26,680 --> 00:17:27,880
An incurable illness

299
00:17:28,840 --> 00:17:29,880
is one's fate.

300
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:34,140
Then I'll change my fate.

301
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:37,600
For 800 years,

302
00:17:38,080 --> 00:17:40,560
only three people have ever succeeded
in changing their fate.

303
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:42,080
They were all remarkable.

304
00:17:43,810 --> 00:17:44,940
That's a good thing.

305
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:47,280
I want to try.

306
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:52,560
Then go to Shendu.

307
00:17:52,920 --> 00:17:55,080
Become the first
in the Imperial Court Exam,

308
00:17:55,080 --> 00:17:57,340
and you'll find a way to change your fate.

309
00:18:22,520 --> 00:18:23,600
I believe in you.

310
00:18:23,710 --> 00:18:24,350
Good luck.

311
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:26,660
I'll wait for your return.

312
00:18:31,320 --> 00:18:32,760
I see.

313
00:18:34,160 --> 00:18:34,880
Chen Changsheng,

314
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:35,740
I'm impressed!

315
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:37,120
From now on,

316
00:18:37,520 --> 00:18:39,050
I'm your brother in Shendu.

317
00:18:40,880 --> 00:18:43,080
But you are just a newcomer
from the mountains,

318
00:18:43,080 --> 00:18:45,210
why is Tiandao Academy picking on you?

319
00:18:45,840 --> 00:18:48,840
Is it because of the marriage contract
you just mentioned?

320
00:18:48,840 --> 00:18:49,840
Which lady is it?

321
00:18:51,560 --> 00:18:53,420
Her home should be here in Shendu.

322
00:18:53,520 --> 00:18:54,780
Her name is Xu Yourong.

323
00:18:56,520 --> 00:18:57,520
Xu Yourong?

324
00:18:58,840 --> 00:18:59,720
You know her?

325
00:19:02,040 --> 00:19:03,120
Xu Yourong.

326
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:07,730
The True Phoenix Blood awakened within her
at the age of ten,

327
00:19:08,080 --> 00:19:10,400
and she's known as the greatest genius
on the Continent.

328
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:12,120
The current
number one of the Blue Cloud List,

329
00:19:12,120 --> 00:19:13,520
and the future Saintess.

330
00:19:16,840 --> 00:19:18,540
She's your fiancée?

331
00:19:18,640 --> 00:19:19,480
Are you sure?

332
00:19:20,080 --> 00:19:21,280
In my memory,

333
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:24,840
she was just a playful child,

334
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:27,680
always bragging to me in her letters.

335
00:19:36,240 --> 00:19:38,100
So she has become so outstanding.

336
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:42,480
No wonder the Academy rejected you.

337
00:19:42,680 --> 00:19:46,080
The Divine General's Estate must know
you're here in Shendu.

338
00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:49,840
The Divine General's Estate
is extremely powerful here.

339
00:19:49,840 --> 00:19:50,920
If word gets out

340
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:54,200
that Xu Yourong has a marriage contract
with a boy from the middle of nowhere,

341
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:57,160
their reputation will be ruined.

342
00:19:58,410 --> 00:20:00,740
Especially that father-in-law of yours,

343
00:20:01,480 --> 00:20:02,480
Xu Shiji,

344
00:20:03,670 --> 00:20:05,620
he's famous for being ruthless.

345
00:20:05,800 --> 00:20:07,530
You wouldn't want to cross him.

346
00:20:10,120 --> 00:20:12,600
I never intended to use this contract
to bind Miss Xu.

347
00:20:12,600 --> 00:20:14,400
I mustn't cause her any trouble.

348
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:17,740
I should've
returned the marriage contract first.

349
00:20:18,880 --> 00:20:19,920
Stop!

350
00:20:27,090 --> 00:20:28,650
Hand over the contract,

351
00:20:28,720 --> 00:20:30,180
and get out of Shendu!

352
00:20:29,570 --> 00:20:32,070
[Xu Shiji, Divine General of the East]

353
00:20:30,480 --> 00:20:31,320
Otherwise,

354
00:20:31,600 --> 00:20:34,000
you won't see the sun tomorrow!

355
00:20:35,390 --> 00:20:39,500
[Tofu Pudding]

356
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:37,280
I was already planning to return it.

357
00:20:37,280 --> 00:20:39,600
May I give it to Miss Xu in person?

358
00:20:40,560 --> 00:20:41,880
Just give it to me.

359
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:43,200
I wish to give it to her myself,

360
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:44,580
and thank her in person.

361
00:20:44,800 --> 00:20:46,460
If it weren't for her letters—

362
00:20:48,280 --> 00:20:51,360
You want my daughter to return
from the Saintess Peak,

363
00:20:51,360 --> 00:20:53,680
and make it public

364
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:56,640
so that you can cling to our estate?

365
00:20:57,120 --> 00:20:59,080
What a despicable man!

366
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:00,970
That's not my intention at all!

367
00:21:02,120 --> 00:21:03,200
Black Unicorn,

368
00:21:03,200 --> 00:21:04,260
violent by nature.

369
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,960
According to the Scriptures,

370
00:21:07,960 --> 00:21:09,690
its weaknesses should be at...

371
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:12,560
Wujin,

372
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:13,410
Baofeng,

373
00:21:13,520 --> 00:21:14,080
Ganshu!

374
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:23,280
Merely some dirty tricks.

375
00:21:26,320 --> 00:21:28,640
You aren't even a cultivator,

376
00:21:28,760 --> 00:21:30,800
do you really think you can fight me?

377
00:21:38,060 --> 00:21:40,070
[Autumn Rain Array-Breaking Saber]

378
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:43,050
Autumn Rain Array-Breaking Saber,

379
00:21:43,050 --> 00:21:44,130
once unsheathed,

380
00:21:44,480 --> 00:21:46,200
its Qi will appear
from all directions,

381
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:47,730
and is impossible to dodge!

382
00:21:49,040 --> 00:21:51,880
I'll give you one last chance.

383
00:21:57,760 --> 00:21:59,720
I only wish to return it

384
00:22:00,080 --> 00:22:01,410
and thank her in person.

385
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:10,920
The Three Thousand Daoist Scriptures

386
00:22:10,920 --> 00:22:12,780
contain everything in the world.

387
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:18,800
Every trick

388
00:22:19,080 --> 00:22:20,560
must have a solution!

389
00:22:21,600 --> 00:22:22,880
The only way out...

390
00:22:22,810 --> 00:22:23,180
[Qingshu, Lieque]

391
00:22:23,680 --> 00:22:24,180
[Zhenshu, Tingguang]

392
00:22:24,430 --> 00:22:24,870
[Xuanshu, Tiangu]

393
00:22:25,280 --> 00:22:25,670
[Ruishu, Jinshe]

394
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:29,960
is forward!

395
00:22:35,120 --> 00:22:36,120
This brat

396
00:22:36,500 --> 00:22:39,830
used gold needles to draw down lightning
and break my array!

397
00:22:56,760 --> 00:22:58,120
That short sword,

398
00:22:58,400 --> 00:22:59,640
that scabbard,

399
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,760
and that aura...

400
00:23:04,080 --> 00:23:06,320
He's weird all over.

401
00:23:06,420 --> 00:23:10,180
[Army Breaker]

402
00:23:08,120 --> 00:23:09,880
He can't be allowed to live.

403
00:23:24,360 --> 00:23:25,690
Xu Shiji's Star Domain?

404
00:23:26,080 --> 00:23:27,240
This is getting out of hand!

405
00:23:27,240 --> 00:23:27,720
Crap!

406
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:30,880
My daughter has the True Phoenix Blood,

407
00:23:30,880 --> 00:23:32,680
she is one of a kind in this world!

408
00:23:32,760 --> 00:23:33,800
So

409
00:23:33,800 --> 00:23:35,330
that means I deserve to die?

410
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:39,680
Everyone

411
00:23:40,120 --> 00:23:40,920
is one of a kind

412
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:42,760
in this world!

413
00:23:44,160 --> 00:23:46,200
I originally
intended to return the marriage contract.

414
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:47,080
But now...

415
00:23:47,240 --> 00:23:48,760
If I can break your saber array,

416
00:23:48,760 --> 00:23:50,360
I can break your Star Domain.

417
00:24:14,320 --> 00:24:16,920
Lord Xu's saber is as fast as always.

418
00:24:17,050 --> 00:24:18,710
[Mo Yu, Chief Imperial Official]

419
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:22,280
I almost didn't make it in time.

420
00:24:22,800 --> 00:24:24,440
Miss Mo Yu,

421
00:24:24,720 --> 00:24:27,160
I'm just handling some family matters.

422
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:28,840
Why are you interfering,

423
00:24:28,880 --> 00:24:30,400
Miss Mo?

424
00:24:37,560 --> 00:24:39,240
I, of course,
will not meddle in your family matters,

425
00:24:39,240 --> 00:24:40,870
Lord Xu.

426
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:44,060
I'm here to deliver
the Grand Pontiff's Divine Decree.

427
00:24:50,600 --> 00:24:52,640
By the order
of the Grand Pontiff of Shendu,

428
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:53,440
I proclaim:

429
00:24:53,840 --> 00:24:56,360
Chen Changsheng of Xining

430
00:24:59,400 --> 00:25:00,560
shall stay in Shendu

431
00:25:00,760 --> 00:25:02,960
and enter the State Religious Academy!

432
00:25:03,880 --> 00:25:05,080
How is that possible?

433
00:25:05,120 --> 00:25:07,380
He's just a commoner from the mountains!

434
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:12,000
Lord Xu,

435
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:14,720
surely you wouldn't want
to defy the Divine Decree

436
00:25:14,720 --> 00:25:16,760
for something like this?

437
00:25:18,480 --> 00:25:19,640
Grand Pontiff...

438
00:25:21,040 --> 00:25:23,240
Could you really break his Star Domain?

439
00:25:23,400 --> 00:25:24,260
I was bluffing.

440
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:29,500
Master, Senior Yuren,

441
00:25:30,120 --> 00:25:31,520
it's a new day.

442
00:25:33,920 --> 00:25:35,050
Where are you going?

443
00:25:39,880 --> 00:25:42,360
To see the sunrise of the new day.

444
00:25:58,060 --> 00:25:59,150
You've been watching for so long,

445
00:25:59,150 --> 00:26:01,060
why not join the State Religious Academy?

446
00:26:01,060 --> 00:26:03,460
Remember to scan the code
to register here!

447
00:26:04,630 --> 00:26:06,060
The Imperial Court Exam
is only three months away,

448
00:26:05,170 --> 00:26:08,590
[In the next episode]

449
00:26:06,300 --> 00:26:08,260
isn't it too late
to begin your cultivation now?

450
00:26:08,260 --> 00:26:10,120
If you already know life is short,

451
00:26:10,130 --> 00:26:11,250
isn't it better

452
00:26:11,800 --> 00:26:12,730
to live in peace?

453
00:26:13,450 --> 00:26:14,590
Master Meilisha,

454
00:26:15,070 --> 00:26:16,200
I truly can't handle

455
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:19,290
this young Director Chen.

456
00:26:19,900 --> 00:26:22,130
My Divine Consciousness
might be destroyed, and I may die.

457
00:26:22,130 --> 00:26:22,500
But

458
00:26:23,030 --> 00:26:25,190
this is only the first step to changing my fate!

